{"tid":667197,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"《鬼神童子》漫畫作者黑岩善宏因病去世 年僅55歲","createTime":"2018-05-16T14:00:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-15T15:31:04.000Z","uid":49391,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a9bbba63b75958ff81bc68ffd56d13626ad7f004","tid":667197,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T14:00:42.000Z","msg":"今天（5月16日），日本媒體又公開了一個讓人惋惜的消息，經典少年漫畫《鬼神童子ZENKI》作者黑岩善宏因突發心肌梗塞，於5月8日去世，年僅55歲。他的個人推特也正式公開了這個消息，漫迷們也紛紛留言祈願黑岩善宏老師一路走好。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/05/20180516_lr_176_2/gamersky_01small_02_20185161050EF7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F05%2F20180516_lr_176_2%2Fgamersky_01small_02_20185161050EF7.jpg&h=4690321b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/05/20180516_lr_176_2/gamersky_02small_04_20185161050440.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F05%2F20180516_lr_176_2%2Fgamersky_02small_04_20185161050440.jpg&h=756975fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　黑岩善宏是日本老一輩漫畫家，其筆下作品有《鬼神童子》、《魔神龍》、《怪奇陰陽路》等。可以說是一個典型的神魔類漫畫家。黑岩善宏最著名的作品就是《鬼神童子》了，這部漫畫推出過多款遊戲與一部動畫，曾經在許多人中刮起了一陣鬼神熱潮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img1.gamersky.com/image2018/05/20180516_lr_176_2/gamersky_03small_06_20185161050855.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fimage2018%2F05%2F20180516_lr_176_2%2Fgamersky_03small_06_20185161050855.jpg&h=d3bfb46f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"11cd369800885986d713cc084c0e8298243c3205","tid":667197,"uid":3063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T14:03:29.000Z","msg":"食粒乜嘢果<br />\n手肘有條刺用黎插人"},{"pid":"7d0feac25a19e3949a060d222a4fa61effc6b6d7","tid":667197,"uid":1928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T14:05:20.000Z","msg":"D畫風咁似"},{"pid":"4574d98af9780a3efdfe0687a47f2a7287ebf2a8","tid":667197,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"